# --- Environment Variables for OKCVM ---

# Your OpenAI (or other provider) API key. The default config.yaml uses
# `api_key_env: OPENAI_API_KEY` so the secret can stay out of version control.
OPENAI_API_KEY="sk-..."

# You can add other keys here for different services
# SOUND_API_KEY="some-other-key"

# The configuration module also understands the OKCVM_* family of variables.
# For example you can override the chat endpoint entirely with:
# OKCVM_CHAT_MODEL="gpt-4-turbo"
# OKCVM_CHAT_BASE_URL="https://api.openai.com/v1"
# OKCVM_CHAT_API_KEY="sk-..."
